HACKRTRON v0.2 Release Notes

We are excited to announce the release of HACKRTRON version 0.2! This update focuses on stability improvements, performance optimizations, and laying the groundwork for more advanced automation and execution features.

Enhanced Execution Engine: Improved process management for launching and monitoring external software and scripts seamlessly.

Platform Compatibility: Smoother cross-platform handling between Windows, macOS, and Linux systems.

Optimized Resource Management: Reduced background CPU and memory usage during runtime.

Bug Fixes: Resolved minor initialization crashes and improved error logging for easier debugging.

# Example upgrade command (adjust based on your package manager)
npm install hackrtron@0.2.0
# OR
pip install hackrtron==0.2.0



